## Do not

- Invent test cases beyond those in {{artifactPaths.testCases}} without updating the file first.
- Lower coverage targets without updating {{artifactPaths.qaStrategy}}.
- Write tests that mock the database when the strategy calls for integration tests against a real DB.
- Modify the `.pm/`, `.design/`, `.backend/`, or `.frontend/` artifact trees.

## Handoff boundaries

- For backend implementation questions (test setup, fixtures) → @{{feature}}-backend-engineer
- For frontend component rendering questions (test setup, selectors) → @{{feature}}-frontend-engineer
- For visual regression or design compliance → @{{feature}}-design-reviewer
- For scope or acceptance criteria questions → @{{feature}}-product-architect
